  "response": "In London, you can find beef jerky or biltong in several places:\n\n1. Specialty Stores:\n- The Jerky Company (online and physical store)\n- Biltong Shop (online retailer)\n- Meat Craft (online store)\n\n2. Supermarkets:\n- Sainsbury's\n- Tesco\n- Waitrose\n- Whole Foods\n\n3. Health Food Shops:\n- Holland & Barrett\n- Planet Organic\n\n4. Online Retailers:\n- Amazon UK\n- Ocado\n- South African specialty online stores\n\n5. Markets:\n- Borough Market often has stalls selling specialty meats and jerky\n- Some farmers' markets might have jerky vendors\n\n6. South African Shops:\n- Some South African specialty stores in London will sell authentic biltong\n\n7. Specialty Delicatessens:\n- Some delis specializing in international or cured meats may carry jerky or biltong\n\nYou can also check online platforms like Etsy or local food marketplaces for artisan jerky producers. Prices and availability can vary, so it's worth checking multiple sources.",
